  "title": "Allocation Strategy Process Flow",
  "content": "\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"hiq-page-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"hiq-t-wrap\">\r\n\t\t\r\n  \t  <div class=\"hiq-t \">\r\n\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"breadcrumbs\"><li><a class=\"breadcrumb-links\" hqid=\"1788908\"  href=\"/home\">Home</a></li> <li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"3500947\" href=\"/supply-chain-planning\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Manhattan Active® Supply Chain Planning</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"3500948\" href=\"/process-configuration-guides-5\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Process &amp; Configuration Guides</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"3500976\" href=\"/allocation-3\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Allocation</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"3660886\" href=\"/new-folder-1752486223\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Allocation Configuration</a></li><li> <span>››</span>Allocation Strategy Process Flow</li></ul>  \t\r\n\t\t<h3>Allocation Strategy Process Flow</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"1\">The allocation strategy process is used to specify the business rules that will govern an allocation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"102\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"102\">The process&nbsp;can be broken into the following steps:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul data-indent-level=\"1\">\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"158\">Distribution center and Location priority sequence - the distribution centers will be selected for the strategy. The priority for locations (grade or minimum need-based) is also specified at this stage.</p>\r\n\t</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"374\">Policy configuration - business rules for picking items and stores for allocation are specified.</p>\r\n\t</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"493\">Phase configuration - business rules that will govern the allocation parameters like pack rounding, constraints, inventory holdback %, etc can be specified in this stage.</p>\r\n\t</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"671\">Users can specify different parameters for each phase of the item lifecycle, including pre-season, in-season, and end-of-season.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img height=\"342\" src=\"https://dzf8vqv24eqhg.cloudfront.net/userfiles/4665/33886/ckfinder/images/Allocation%20Strategy%20Process%20flow.png?Policy=eyJTdGF0ZW1lbnQiOlt7IlJlc291cmNlIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9kemY4dnF2MjRlcWhnLmNsb3VkZnJvbnQubmV0L3VzZXJmaWxlcy80NjY1LzMzODg2L2NrZmluZGVyL2ltYWdlcy9BbGxvY2F0aW9uJTIwU3RyYXRlZ3klMjBQcm9jZXNzJTIwZmxvdy5wbmciLCJDb25kaXRpb24iOnsiRGF0ZUxlc3NUaGFuIjp7IkFXUzpFcG9jaFRpbWUiOjE3NTQ3NTQxNzJ9fX1dfQ__&Signature=TGuUdVLVv2u0nmX01ipUfkKmUCuIZ~woUg-YsiyFIggIck~bQQvdz528PKcGtNODdO87b29FC-XVLBtK1w-uvtqlsV4JcmcdSmYZK8M78y5CMvzMJ2V8gw9~DhW3y1ueT6ZYhB~pW6MbMaC6D6pHeSZ4gd0JLz9DffV3TcQaY7e8N69xpsE1Ot9vS4OdxlUVclXyQi5UoRbMeQmY~yIlJJIAoij5IxCdtEoRzTYb3bbeijIc4YhpPcmV9qjouV~dZcDaQpYYS0aomjF8f3pIdf~FMFw2feGnQFzheVtY6S3BYYkPs9Rt68MRJeHB3qgveh-uinsEwsxHAtCXJj6MpQ__&Key-Pair-Id=K2TK3EG287XSFC\" style=\"width: 979px; height: 327px;\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"\" style=\"left: 107.6px; top: 85.4px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"\" style=\"left: 107.6px; top: 85.4px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"\" style=\"left: 107.6px; top: 85.4px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n\t  </div>\r\n </div>\r\n <div id=\"ui-page-fb-wrap\"></div>\r\n <div class=\"hiq-footer-wrap\">\r\n    \r\n                \r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
